^B@2^*BMarty Bergen: ^*N|cp||at|North has a terrific hand, particularly in support of spades. He’s very interested in slam; in fact, even seven is possible. So he’ll respond 2NT, and East will pass.|MB|2N|AN|Asking for feature|
