NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*BMarty Bergen: ^*N|cp||at|You see the way I set up the hand, West has both spades; so the finesse will succeed. And you may say, “Marty, that’s very convenient to make your point, but it certainly didn’t have to be that way.” And I’ll agree with that.|
